parameters:
Leviathan Well, it's about time to say
goodbye.

Leviathan This time, I will definitely seize
happiness.
Masamune Hey, tell me your name before we part.

Leviathan Is that so... well, I guess it's
fine.
Masamune Wait for me after all.

Leviathan Don't stop! We're at a good part
right now.

Masamune I'm definitely going to stop using
magic. There's no need to go back.
Leviathan What! At this point... you coward!

Masamune I'm not a coward. It's because going
back is harder.

Masamune Leviathan... no, it's harder when
Hannah is gone.

Hanna Don't say stupid things. You've been
working hard to help Amelia, right?

Masamune Until now, I've been desperately
working hard without thinking about anything
else.

Masamune Even though I was the one who started
dating her... I was desperately trying to get back
the one I love, Amelia.

Masamune Towards the end, I had some thoughts
about Amelia's attitude... but it's my fault.

Masamune I've become a prisoner of pleasure...
that's because we kept repeating the loop.

Masamune It's because I was attacked by the
demon dog at first, and then I was cursed by
Hoffman...
Hanna Don't blame yourself too much...

Masamune It's not like I've come to dislike
Amelia. I just started thinking that maybe it
would be better for both of us to be apart.

Hanna To say that you want to be in a
relationship with me right away... it's completely
unreasonable.

Masamune No, I didn't say I want to date you. I
just said it's painful when you're gone.
Hanna Y-Yes, I see. I had misunderstood.
Hanna Forget about what just happened.

Masamune ...Do you want to be in a relationship
with Hanna?

Hanna We've been together for a long time... so
it would be lonely for me to be separated from
Masamune.

Hanna But being in a relationship... that's not
something for now.
Hanna Masamune and I are partners, you know.

Masamune You were my partner? That's the first
time I've heard that.

Hanna Since we've been cooperating with each
other, the word 'partner' is probably the most
fitting.
Hanna It's fine if we separate.

Hanna So... you're really not going to take it
back?

Masamune Can we continue to be together from
now on?
Hanna Alright, what are you planning to do?

Masamune I don't know what will happen from now
on, but since we have nowhere else to go, shall we
go on a journey together?

Masamune I am also a sinner who made a contract
with a demon, so it's probably best to stay away
from Great Land.

Hanna Are you planning to take me on a runaway
journey?

Masamune It can't be helped... If I think about
it calmly, being a half-demon, even the Magic
Association wouldn't know what to do.

Hanna Hmm. But I don't want to get caught
anymore. I'm tired of living in a prison cell.
Hanna I have a good idea for that.

Hanna I won't use time reversal magic, but I'll
only use inheritance magic.

Hanna If we do that, both me and Masamune will
lose the power of the Demon Lord.

Hanna Masamune will return to normal, and I
will no longer be a demon.

HannaOnly Masamune's friends know my face. If
they report me, Masamune will be involved too, so
I can live a normal life without any problems.

Hanna If the inheritance magic goes as planned,
it will be a success, but...

Hanna I don't know because I've never done it
before.
Masamune What will happen if it fails...
Hanna That's why I'm saying I don't know.

Masamune No, that's not possible! If Hanna were
to disappear... ...
Masamune I don't want it if it's not 100%.

Hanna But there's no other choice. A life on
the run is difficult.
Hanna Do you really think Masamune can escape?

Hanna If the magic succeeds, I will be able to
live the same amount of time as Masamune and
become human.
Hanna It's the best, the only way.
Masamune Please make sure it's a success.

Hanna The magic has already been activated...
Don't interfere.

Hanna We're partners after all, so don't hug me
like a child.

Masamune If Hanna wasn't here, I would have
given up a long time ago...

Masamune I couldn't handle something this
difficult on my own.

Hanna In the first place, you wouldn't be able
to go back without me.

Masamune Right now... I don't feel lonely at
all.
Hanna ...Don't worry. Everything will be fine.

Masamune Then tell me it will be 100%
successful.
Hanna I don't want to lie.
Hanna But I am a genius of magic.
